# Zig Build System
zig init-exe          - Initialize a new executable project
zig init-lib          - Initialize a new library project
zig build             - Build the project using build.zig
zig build test        - Run the tests for the project

# Zig Commands
zig run <file.zig>    - Compile and run a Zig source file
zig test <file.zig>   - Compile and run tests in a Zig source file
zig fmt .             - Format all Zig source code in the current directory

# Zig Cross-compilation
zig build -Dtarget=x86_64-windows -Drelease-safe - Compile for Windows
zig build -Dtarget=aarch64-macos -Drelease-safe  - Compile for ARM macOS
